ThmSignature
  signFrom ThmStatement
  signTo ThmStatement
  deriving Show Eq Read

Thm
  category ThmCategory
  content Text
  proof Text Maybe
  name Text Maybe
  sign ThmSignature
  ref Text Maybe
  note Text Maybe
  deriving Eq Show

User
    ident Text
    password Text Maybe
    UniqueUser ident

Email
    email Text
    user UserId Maybe
    verkey Text Maybe
    UniqueEmail email

Person
  personName Text
  personBirthday Day
  personFavoriteColor Text Maybe
  personEmail Text
  personWebsite Text Maybe
  UniquePersonEmail personEmail
  deriving Eq Show

 -- By default this file is used in Model.hs (which is imported by Foundation.hs)
